OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,FUnresolved household complaints to
OL,7,Fwater firms have spiked amid
OL,8,Fdiscontent over sewage spills, billing
OL,9,Fmistakes and problems with water
OL,10,Fmeters, an annual report shows.
OL,12,FThe number of complaints escalated to
OL,13,Fthe Consumer Council for Water (CCW)
OL,14,Fby households in England and Wales who
OL,15,Ffailed to achieve a resolution from
OL,16,Ftheir supplier rose by almost a third
OL,17,F(29%) in 2023-24 ` its highest level
OL,18,Ffor nearly a decade, the watchdog said.
