OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,FConcerns about firms' environmental
OL,7,Fperformance and water meters had
OL,8,Ffuelled the steep increase, with
OL,9,Fcustomers having exhausted their
OL,10,Fsupplier's two-stage complaints
OL,11,Fprocess by the time they turned to the
OL,12,FCCW.
OL,14,FCCW's annual report shows that
OL,15,Fcustomers made a total of 222,956
OL,16,Fcomplaints directly to water companies
OL,17,Fin England and Wales.
