OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,FWithin the 7,977 cases received by
OL,7,FCCW, complaints about environmental
OL,8,Fissues spiked by 217% over the last 12
OL,9,Fmonths, mainly relating to spills from
OL,10,Fstorm overflows and wider pollution of
OL,11,Frivers and seas.
OL,13,FIssues relating to water meters rose
OL,14,Fby 30%, including concerns over how
OL,15,Foften they were being read and whether
OL,16,Fthey were working properly.
