OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,F"More companies are planning to roll
OL,7,Fout smart meters over the next few
OL,8,Fyears, so they must listen and act on
OL,9,Fpeople's concerns now or risk further
OL,10,Fdamaging customer trust."
OL,12,FDavid Bird, retail director at Thames
OL,13,FWater, said: "We are committed to
OL,14,Fimproving the experience of our
OL,15,Fcustomers and have been working
OL,16,Fclosely alongside CCW to address these
OL,17,Fissues.
