OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,F"A better measure is the number of
OL,7,Fcomplaints sent by the Consumer
OL,8,FCouncil for Water to adjudication,
OL,9,Fwhich fell 37%, from 153 late last
OL,10,Fyear to 57 for the equivalent period
OL,11,Fthis year."
OL,13,FCCW's report comes amid mounting
OL,14,Fpublic and political fury around
OL,15,Ffirms' polluting of waterways with
OL,16,Fsewage spills as they continue to hand
OL,17,Fdividends to shareholders, and bonuses
OL,18,Fto executives ` something which Labour
OL,19,Fhas pledged to clamp down on.
