OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,FSewage spills into England's rivers
OL,7,Fand seas more than doubled in 2023.
OL,9,FAccording to the Environment Agency,
OL,10,Fthere were 3.6 million hours of spills
OL,11,Flast year ` equal to about 400 years `
OL,12,Fcompared with 1.75 million hours in
OL,13,F2022.
OL,15,FEarlier this year, Ofwat revealed #168
OL,16,Fmillion of proposed fines for three of
OL,17,FEngland's biggest water companies for
OL,18,Ffailing to manage sewage spills,
OL,19,Fincluding a #104 million penalty for
OL,20,Ftroubled Thames Water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
