OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,FThe fine for Thames came alongside a
OL,7,Fplanned #47 million penalty for
OL,8,FYorkshire Water and #17 million for
OL,9,FNorthumbrian Water after a "catalogue
OL,10,Fof failure" by the firms, according to
OL,11,FOfwat in the first batch of results
OL,12,Ffrom its biggest ever investigation
OL,13,Finto the industry.
OL,15,FIn July, Ofwat proposed that water
OL,16,Ffirms should be allowed to increase
OL,17,Fbills by a third less than they had
OL,18,Frequested on average.
