OL,6,FWater firms had put forward plans for
OL,7,Fincreases averaging #144 over five
OL,8,Fyears, although there were significant
OL,9,Fvariations in price changes between
OL,10,Fsuppliers.
OL,12,FOfwat said its proposals to cap the
OL,13,Faverage bill increase at 21% ` around
OL,14,F#19 per year ` follows firms'
OL,15,Fproposals to increase their total
OL,16,Fspending by #29 billion, split between
OL,17,Fa #5 billion increase in the core
OL,18,Fcosts for running their business and a
OL,19,F#24 billion rise in spending to meet
OL,20,Frequirements set by governments and
OL,21,Ffor other environmental improvements.
