OL,3,CThames Water found to be worst
OL,4,Cperforming water company for complaints
OL,6,FIn its response to Ofwat's draft
OL,7,Fdetermination on water companies'
OL,8,Fplans, Thames proposed raising average
OL,9,Fyearly water bills to #666.50 per
OL,10,Fcustomer by 2030, a 52% rise.
OL,12,FThat could rise to #696, a 59%
OL,13,Fincrease, if it is given extra
OL,14,Fspending allowances by the regulator.
OL,16,FOfwat said it will consider all
OL,17,Fresponses "carefully" ahead of its
OL,18,Ffinal decision on water firms'
OL,19,Fspending plans by December 19.
